OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMicrosoft recognises first 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Flabour union in US         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Workers at Microsoft's ZeniMax Studios 
OL,6, have voted to form the tech giant's    
OL,7, first labour union in the US.          
OL,9,FMicrosoft agreed to recognise the group
OL,10,Fafter a "supermajority" of workers at  
OL,11,Fthe video game production company      
OL,12,Fsignalled support for the plan, said   
OL,13,Fthe Communications Workers of America  
OL,14,F(CWA) union.                           
OL,16,FZeniMax owns popular games including   
OL,17,FThe Elder Scrolls and Fallout.         
OL,19,FIt follows an uptick in unionisation   
OL,20,Fefforts in the US.                     
